NG0516:1: 'tsho byed gzhon nu'i ldum rar rgyas //
NG0516:2: gdung ba'i shugs kyis mchi ma phyung *//
NG0516:3: kye ma kye hud kye ma klung *//
NG0516:4: ston pa sgron ma'i 'od nub nas //
NG0516:5: sems can mun pa gang gis sel //
NG0516:6: de ltar smre sngags brgyal sangs nas //
NG0516:7: nam mkha'i dbyings su yar bltas pas //
NG0516:9: ston pa drug pa rdo rje 'chang *//
NG0516:10: phyag g.yas grub lo yar byung nas //
NG0516:11: rin chen shel gyi za ma tog / sen gang ba cig mar la bor //
NG0516:12: bdag gis lag g.yon yar brkyang bas //
NG0516:13: glegs bam lag mthil g.yon du babs //
NG0516:14: de nyid zhal phyes ltas pa'i //
NG0516:15: mthing gi shug gu mthing kha la //
NG0516:16: b+hai dur zhun mas bris pa snang *//
NG0516:17: mthong bas dga' rab rang rgyud grol //
NG0516:18: de yi zhal chems 'di ltar ro //
NG0516:19: kye ma kye ma rigs kyi bu //
NG0516:20: gsang sngags gsang ba'i gnad rnams kun //
NG0516:21: gcig tu dril la nyams su long *//
NG0516:22: lus ngag yid kyi sngon 'gro ni //
NG0516:23: mi rtag snying rjes byang sems bsgom //
NG0516:24: dben zhing nyams dga' gnas nyid brten //
NG0516:25: chos dang mthun pa'i mched grogs tshol /
NG0516:26: khams kyi brtan po yo byad bsar //
NG0516:27: sku gsum rten gyi mchod pa shis //
NG0516:28: lus ni ma bcos gang bder 'dug / ngag ni 'chal pa'i lo byung yang *//
NG0516:29: sems rtog snga phyi bar gsum chod //
NG0516:30: 'di ni zhen log drag po bsgom //
NG0516:31: dge med rgyud la yang yang khol //
NG0516:32: lus ngag yid gsum rang sor glod //
NG0516:33: de nas don dam sems skyed ni //
NG0516:34: stong gsal snying rjes bdag med bsgom //
NG0516:35: lus 'di dmigs rgyus bskyed pa'i phyir //
NG0516:36: rigs drug sa bon nyid du gnas //
NG0516:37: rig pa sku gsum dngos yin phyir //
NG0516:38: sku gsum yi ge gsum du gnas //
NG0516:39: ye shes rtsal sbyang ru shan dbye //
NG0516:40: dbye ba rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NG0516:41: thog mar tha mal pa yis lus //
NG0516:42: mdzod spu mgrin pa snying kha dang *//
NG0516:43: lte ba gsang gnas rkang mthil du //
NG0516:44: a dkar ti mthing nr-i ljang dang *//
NG0516:45: bre ser sre dmar du nag sgom //
NG0516:46: sku gsung thugs la 'bru gsum ni //
NG0516:47: dkar dmar mthing la me 'bar bas //
NG0516:48: rigs drug sa bon sreg par bsgom //
NG0516:49: om ahhum gsum la bdun 'bum bskyal //
NG0516:50: des ni ngan song rdog pas non //
NG0516:51: gnyis pa bdag gi rdor sems kyis //
NG0516:52: sku gsung thugs yig 'khor lo bsgom //
NG0516:54: bzhi pa kun rdzob las rim bsgom //
NG0516:56: tshogs gnyis rdzogs phyir man+dal phul //
NG0516:57: byin rlabs 'byung phyir gsol ba btab //
NG0516:58: lus sgrib byang phyir phyag bskor bya //
NG0516:59: ngag sgrib sbyang phyir yig brgya bzlas //
NG0516:60: mdo dang bsngo ba smon lam btab //
NG0516:61: nyin mtshan chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NG0516:62: mgron rigs bzhi la longs spyod 'bul //
NG0516:63: de ltar sngon 'gro rdzogs byas nas //
NG0516:64: spros bcas la sogs dbang rnams @#//
NG0516:66: dbang srog dam tshig sku gsung thugs //
NG0516:67: ma khrel gsum gyi srungs mtshams bca' //
NG0516:68: mya ngan 'das pa'i sna sel yin //
NG0516:70: thar pa bgrod pa'i lam skal yin //
NG0516:71: 'khor ba sgrol ba'i gru chen yin //
NG0516:72: de skad ces ni rang shar ba //
NG0516:73: bstan pa kun gyi snying gzer yin //
NG0516:74: rdo rje 'chang gi 'das rjes mchog / zhal chems dag tu bka' stsal lo //
NG0516:75: dpal sngags kyi srungs ma nag mo khros mas srungs cig / sa ma ya /
